---
layout: default.hbs
subject: You've been invited to the new NKBA.org
---
<span class="preheader">You've been invited to NKBA.org as an employee of \{{ org.name }}</span>
<table class="header" align="center"  width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" bgcolor="#FDFDFE"  border="0">
    <tr>
        <td class="wrapper border-bottom" valign="middle">
            <a href="\{{WEB_URL}}"><img class="logo" border="0" src="\{{WEB_URL}}/nkba-logo@2x.png" alt="NKBA" height="30" width="141"></a>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
<table class="main" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
    <tr>
        <td class="wrapper">
            <table width="100%">
                <tr>
                    <td class="content-block text-4 pt1 " valign="top">
                       <h2 class="bold">You've been invited to join the \{{ org.name }} organization on the new NKBA.org</h2>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                
                <tr>
                    <td class="content-block text-4" valign="top">
                        The National Kitchen & Bath Association (NKBA) is an international non-profit organization that serves and represents the firms and individuals involved in all aspects of the kitchen and bathroom industry.
                    </td>
                </tr>


               <tr>
                    <td class="pb3 text-4" valign="top">   
                        {{> button type="primary" title="Join your organization" url="{{WEB_URL}}/invite/{{token}}" align="left"}}
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
